morey attributes inspiration for invention of the boogie board ( july 7 , 1971 ) to a particular baha'i prayer he kept coming across which included the passage " convey upon me , oh , my god , a thought which will turn this planet into a rose garden.'"surfline bio - tom morey , aka y married marchia nichols , now marchia morey , " mother of bodyboarding " who bore them four sons : sol , moon , sky and matteson .   tom sold morey boogie in 1977 and lived in hawaii for a decade , working as a consultant by day , jazz musician by night .

